make build options:
SWE_SDL12 - SDL1.2 support
SWE_WITH_JSON - add json format
SWE_WITH_LUA - add lua support
SWE_EXAMPLES - build examples
SWE_DLOPEN - add load shared libs support, with -ldl
SWE_DISABLE_NETWORK - disable SDL_net
SWE_DISABLE_AUDIO - disable SDL_mixer (mp3, ogg support disabled)
SWE_DISABLE_IMAGE - disable SDL_image (load tif, jpg, png disabled)
SWE_DISABLE_TTF - disable SDL_ttf (builtin alt-8x16.psf used only)
SWE_DISABLE_TERMGUI - disable build termwin_gui
SWE_DEBUG_MESSAGES - DEBUG works
SWE_STACKTRACE - stack trace on exception
